  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Sometimes when \"Send transaction\" screen is opened it does not show recipient, wallet or amount fields. It looks like the screen is being scrolled when the keyboard appears. The screen can be fixed by scrolling it a little bit in any direction.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/34745095-aca01eb2-f58f-11e7-94ae-28b1d6e6c3c1.png)\r\n\r\nOr sometimes:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/34745434-cdbdf41a-f590-11e7-866c-66f3c229dfef.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nShowing keyboard should not break the scroll in \"Send transaction\" screen. \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nSometimes when keyboard is shown the screen is scrolled and does not show all fields.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Kill Status app\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Wallet\r\n- Click Send\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.12 (TestFlight)\r\n* Operating System: iOS\r\n* Tested on: iPhone 6, iOS 11.2.1\r\n* Can be reproduced 5/7 times. Especially when the app is killed and opened again.\r\n",
